room_title: Escape room "Alcatraz" by Trapped Escape Game in Nashville
review: My cousins and I recently played the “Alcatraz” escape room and had a blast! All three of us had a blast and plan on coming back in the near future to try and conquer “Death Zone” or “Asylum”. Thank you again for a fun night!

room_title: Escape room "Alcatraz" by Trapped Escape Game in Nashville
review: OMGOODNESS! I cannot say enough great things about this place and the staff! They were so friendly. Place is clean. Perfect way to celebrate birthday with the family over the weekend. We needed about another minute to Escape Alcatrez-Not bad for a group of first timers. Definitely will come back. Easy to book online.

room_title: Escape room "Alcatraz" by Trapped Escape Game in Nashville
review: We did the Alcatraz room. With just a few clues from the staff, we were able to conquer and escape!
